reporter_caption.center: THE FLORIDA BAR v. VENTURA, 945 So.2d 1291 (Fla. 2006)

caption.center: THE FLORIDA BAR, Petitioner(s), v. ENRIQUE JORGE VENTURA,

opinion.opinion_text:
Respondent's petition for review filed with this Court on August 14, 2006, is hereby dismissed for failure to file a brief. See Rules Regulating The Florida Bar 37.7(c)(3).
The report of referee filed with this Court on June 19, 2006, is approved and Respondent's Motion to Dissolve Emergency Suspension is denied and the suspension imposed by this Court on May 9, 2006, shall remain in force without amendment, until further order of this Court.
LEWIS, C.J., and WELLS, ANSTEAD, PARIENTE, QUINCE, CANTERO, and BELL, JJ., concur.
